      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FANTASTIC SPIKE (1) hit the ground running from this same draw last time and led all the way to score (30.01) in a Grade 4/5 over 530m at Murray Bridge. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. ZINFANDEL EMMA (4) was in winning form two back (30.57) at Gawler but ran below best last time there, finishing 8th. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won three of five tries. The form out of last run is most impressive. Should be about the money. COOL BLUE YOU (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (26.24) last time in a Grade 6 at Murray Bridge. Has a good record here including three wins. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. Can do much better this time. TRIO OF CLOWNS (2) can feature with the right run.",
